#

Grilled Tofu Steaks with Chimichurri Sauce and Stuffed Acorn Squash

$12.99
450 kcal
Difficulty: 50%

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

GrilledHealthyPlant-Based

Description

Savory grilled tofu paired with a vibrant chimichurri sauce and sweet, roasted acorn squash stuffed with flavorful vegetables.

Ingredients

  • Firm tofu: 14 oz
  • Fresh parsley: 1 cup, chopped
  • Garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • Red wine vinegar: 1/4 cup
  • Olive oil: 1/3 cup
  • Red pepper flakes: 1 tsp
  • Acorn squash: 2 medium
  • Bell pepper: 1, diced
  • Zucchini: 1, diced
  • Black beans: 1 can, rinsed and drained
  • Cumin: 1 tsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
